Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthey were trapped in the Birdcage along with the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Corazon,\Nin order to cure Law's White Lead Disease,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}took him out and went around various hospitals\Nfor six months.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do to me?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a rude little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and hearing you say "I'll die soon" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...heartbreaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... stabbed me... that day but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it didn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you were the one who was in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Time is Ticking Down!\NSeize the Op-Op Fruit!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! It didn't cut it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be wasting my time here\Nany longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it can't be cut by a sword,\Nhow about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...\N--Hey, Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}! Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...\N--I like how it sounds. Call me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick it up! The Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me, Corazon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon, you're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been six months since you two left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Law with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. I'm glad both of you are okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you found a good doctor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Law and come back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We might be able to cure the disease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got information about the Op-Op Fruit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Offered a huge amount of money\Nby the Navy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}some stupid pirates who don't know its value\Nwill accept a tradeoff, it seems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government must be pulling the strings\Nbehind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's risky but we'll seize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once we get it,\Nbecause of the nature of its power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the person I trust the most should eat it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You eat it, Corazon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And cure Law's disease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even including Tsuru who often smelled out where we were\Nand came after us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy hasn't showed their face at all\Nin the past six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six months that Corazon was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\Nhe was tipping the Navy off before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.\NI don't want to distrust him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my biological brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good news! Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a chance to survive!\NForget about foolish doctors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get the Op-Op Fruit,\Nwe'd be able to cure your White Lead Disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Op-Op Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives you the ability to\Nmodify human bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can perform miraculous operations\Nand cure even unknown diseases with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in that magic crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's no magic!\NYou need medical knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're the son of a doctor\Nwho was trusted by the people of Flevance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the time you were able to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were learning medical knowledge and techniques,\Nweren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah but...\Nwhat does it have to do with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's perfect for you to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!\NDoflamingo said you should eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person will die\Nif he eats two Devil Fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy said that because he doesn't know\Nthat I'm a Devil Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I...\NWe won't go back to the Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided so when I noticed\Nthis journey would take longer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Doffy knows that \NI'm a traitor by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't sound like it.\NHe said you should eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is another reason for Doffy to say\Nhe wants me to eat the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doffy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I won't refuse you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're looking to have eternal life \Nin exchange for my life, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get killed if I go back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we'll get a jump on Doffy and the others\Nand steal the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat the Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get cured,\Nlet's go hide somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to set sail!\NWe'll get the Op-Op Fruit at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Clank.\N--{\i1}"Rice crackers"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rice-cracker pellets"! It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rosinante! It's been a while.\NI've been worried about you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Garp!\NWhy don't you go out for a sec?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! I just brought you senbei crackers!\NMake green tea for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vice Admiral Garp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't a good time, Sengoku-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get out! Idiot!\NI gotta work! W-O-R-K!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:58.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!\NHow dare he treat me like a nuisance! Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kuzan!\NDo you wanna eat {\i1}senbei{\i0} crackers with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um... Can I talk?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have a deal regarding\Nthe Op-Op Fruit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But it's top secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cora-san must be talking to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know those pirates' activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think we can find them\Nbefore the trade...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Doflamingo is looking to\Nsteal the Op-Op Fruit before the trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it true?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh? Hm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kind of feel dizzy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When and where will the trade be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three weeks from now,\Nat Rubeck in the North Blue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rubeck...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet up with Doffy and the others\Nat Swallow Island three days before the handoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three days before, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I guess all of the Family members\Nwill wait for the fight there for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a good tip.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be it for Doflamingo!\NWe'll ambush at Swallow Island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and catch the Donquixote Family\Nin one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay away from the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The list of all Doffy's business partners\Nand the big names
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,connected with him behind the scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's enough for you to uncover...\Nthe dark side of the North Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay. Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Law. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta sail out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! Hey! You gotta be kidding!\NStay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now! We finally got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not been three years yet!\NI thought you still had time left according to your calculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He has a very high fever!\NWhat should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctors are all useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Let's give him some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?!\NTell me, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alive for another three weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a chance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:54.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THREE DAYS BEFORE THE TRADE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:50.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why does it have \Nto be so choppy now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government knew that we would die
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut they kept making us dig up White Lead, for money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family... and the people of Flevance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you're a Navy soldier allied with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd! I'm not a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact... You need to realize -\NStealing the Op-Op Fruit means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll make enemies of everybody...\NDoflamingo, the Navy, and the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be chased by all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be prepared to fight to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:13.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MINION ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found the pirates, Sengoku-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, east of Rubeck \Nwhere we'll have a trade,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's Minion Island which has a ghost town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like that's where their hideout is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diez Barrels is the pirate's name.\NSounds familiar?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's a former Navy officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our look-out ship is staking out\NMinion Island now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all as Sengoku-san said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, at Swallow Island\Nwhere you and Doflamingo were going to meet up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there are two warships.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think anyone can see here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let Doflamingo steal the Op-Op Fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, it won't be long. Wait here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drie! Booze! Bring more booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think\Nthis one fruit would cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They offered five billion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ridiculous!\NDid the Government go nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we got that much money,\Nthere's no reason for us to be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may sound too simple but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...once a doctor eats this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll become a famous doctor\Nin great demand all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a legendary doctor who ate this\Nand cured intractable or rare diseases...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by performing miraculous operations,\Nthey say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it has nothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, getting money is way better!\N--That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will cause anything I interact with\Nto not make any noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO SOUND!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NO SOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The direction of his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO SOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You heard nothing, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that ability good for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby 5's Arms-Arms is\Nmuch better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! You're right!\NI wish I had that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can have a quiet sleep like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that quake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Th-There wasn't any noise\Nbut the compound's exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure house is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there an invader?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The lights went off!\N--Pieces of glass are falling onto us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lamps! The lamps are broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Somebody put on a light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put on a light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO SOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...\N--Is that... what that guy did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got it, Law! It's the Op-Op Fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your disease will be cured!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?!\N--Who's this?! He freaked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he tumble down from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NA guy in a black coat stole the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy in a black coat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law, I can't take you with me from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard but... \Nwait here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Corazon seized the Op-Op Fruit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when he reaches to Law,\Nhis body has already exceeded its limit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save Corazon,\NLaw desperately looks for help{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but when a Navy soldier \Nshows up in front of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe wheel of fortune begins to spin out of control!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.29,0:23:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N"The Moment of Resolution! Corazon's Farewell Smile!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
